# Uploads Directory

This directory stores uploaded assignment files.

Files are organized by user ID:
```
uploads/
  └── {userId}/
      ├── timestamp-file1.pdf
      ├── timestamp-file2.jpg
      └── timestamp-file3.docx
```

## Important Notes

- This directory is ignored by git (except this .gitkeep file)
- Maximum file size: 10MB per file
- Maximum files per assignment: 5
- Allowed types: JPG, PNG, PDF, DOC, DOCX, TXT, ZIP

## Production Recommendation

For production deployments, use cloud storage (AWS S3, Google Cloud Storage) instead of local file storage.
